Manually starts training a NeuralNet with 2 hidden Layers à 20 neurons the Hamming Code Neural Net has the Relu activation function for the first layer and sigmoid for the other layers It is trained in 15 000 epochs with a test in every 10 epochs using 4 (if available) cores Learning rate is 0.5 Batch size is 128 NeuralNet will be written to ".
